    "As we can see in Table 3, the performance measures vary widely depending on the application domain and the goal of the method proposed in each paper.",
    "For example, reward is used as a metric in 9 articles but is computed differently depending on the context.",
    "Concerning electric vehicles, in Sultanuddin et al. (2023), the reward corresponds to a penalty function considering the cost of charging and a departure incentive.",
    "Instead, in wastewater treatment plants (WWTPs), Chen et al. (2021) The papers are grouped according to the main related application domains, as in Table 2.",
